manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.palmapp.master.module_cnt.matching.CntMatchActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

🔥 What will you look like after 30 or 50 years? 
🔥 How your palm reveals secrets about LIFE, LOVE & CAREER? 
The new app for 👵🏻 Aging Shutter, ✋🏻 Palm Reading, ✨ Horoscope, 🎴 Tarot Card and ❓ Psycho Tests is out now on Google Play Store.
👵🏻 ★ AGING SHUTTER ★

Wanna know what will you look like in the future?

Upload the current photo, and get your aging faces of 50, 70 or 90 years old.


✋🏻 ★ PALM READING ★ 

Can you read your own palm? Your fate lies in your hands.

By advanced scanning and reading technology, Palm Secret can predict your fortune, love, wealth, marriage and many more aspects.

Palm Secret also uses a very reliable method to read your happiness and your future life from your hand.


✨ ★ HOROSCOPE ★

View detailed report with Love, Health Prediction, Lucky Number, Lucky Color and much more of your horoscope. And you can also know how match your horoscope with others.


 🎴 ★ TAROT CARD★

Read your tarot card of the day for insight and advice for Today.

Beginning every day with Tarot Reading is an awesome method to get psyched for every one of the conceivable outcomes - and evade conceivable traps. Get your report and have an incredible day!


❤️ ★ PSYCHO TESTS ★ 

Are you a romanticist? Will you succeed? Lots of funny tests here!


🤝CONTACT US
